---
---

<section aria-labelledby="core-questions-heading" class="bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-mist-light/50 to-ivory">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20 md:py-28 text-center">
      {/* Visually the eyebrow + intro paragraph serve as the section header;
          add a screen-reader-only h2 so the heading hierarchy stays sequential
          (Hero h1 → here h2 → card h3s), as required by WCAG. */}
      <h2 id="core-questions-heading" class="sr-only">The Questions That Begin Your Awakening</h2>
      <p class="text-gold-ink font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 reveal" aria-hidden="true">The Questions That Begin Your Awakening</p>
      <p class="text-warm-charcoal text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-10 reveal">
        Why do people suffer even when they have everything? Why does the mind create so much chaos? Is there a deeper peace beyond thoughts and emotions? These are the questions that led Master Kaie on her own awakening journey.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12 stagger">
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-card p-8 border border-soft-aura shadow-card hover:shadow-elevated transition-shadow reveal card-calm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-soft-aura rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-violet" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-violet italic mb-3">"Who am I?"</h3>
          <p class="text-body-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Discover your true self beyond the roles, labels, and stories you've been told.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-card p-8 border border-soft-aura shadow-card hover:shadow-elevated transition-shadow reveal card-calm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-soft-aura rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-violet" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-violet italic mb-3">"Why was I born on this earth?"</h3>
          <p class="text-body-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Understand your purpose and the deeper meaning behind your existence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-card p-8 border border-soft-aura shadow-card hover:shadow-elevated transition-shadow reveal card-calm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-soft-aura rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-violet" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-violet italic mb-3">"What is my mission?"</h3>
          <p class="text-body-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Awaken to the unique path and contribution only you can make in this world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-violet/80 italic max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Through the 347 method, you don't receive borrowed answers — you awaken your own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
